Package: win31x
Architecture: any
Provides: x-window-manager
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: default-dbus-session-bus | dbus-session-bus, network-manager,
 xss-lock, xsecurelock, xterm, xfonts-base
Description: minimal Windows 3.1-style window manager for X11
 Win31 X is a small reparenting window manager with classic beveled frames,
 desktop icons for minimized applications, and an installed-application
 launcher. Its Control Panel configures Wi-Fi, color schemes, and automatic
 screen locking, while Windows+R opens a shell-free Run dialog. It supports the
 essential ICCCM lifecycle and a focused EWMH subset.
